      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "oblong-shaped object which alighted in the street in front",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "of him when he was on his way home from his television repair",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "shop, the [REDACTED], Chesapeake,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "Virginia. He believes that he was taken into this craft which",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "he recalls as being made of a glass like substance and being",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
