      "text": "transparent. It was manned by several individuals who appeared",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "to be undersized creatures similar to members of the human",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "race, probably not more than 4 feet tall. They were allegedly",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "wearing regular trouser pants and T-Shirts. [REDACTED] believes",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "that he was transported by this craft for an undetermined",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "distance and returned to his point of take-off approximately",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "one hour later.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "[REDACTED] spoke in a coherent manner although he",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "appeared to be under certain emotional strain. He claimed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "he had not been drinking any intoxicants but he was unable",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "to account for the time between 8:00 p.m. and 4:00 a.m.. He",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
